{
  "local_port": 36938,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some useful websites for students?",
  "response": "There are numerous websites that can be incredibly helpful for students across various subjects and needs. Here\u2019s a categorized list:\n\n### Learning Resources\n1. **Khan Academy** - Offers free courses and practice exercises in various subjects.\n   - Website: [khanacademy.org](https://www.khanacademy.org)\n\n2. **Coursera** - Provides access to courses from universities and organizations, often for free.\n   - Website: [coursera.org](https://www.coursera.org)\n\n3. **edX** - Another platform offering university-level courses in a wide range of subjects.\n   - Website: [edx.org](https://www.edx.org)\n\n4. **Quizlet** - A study tool that allows users to create flashcards and study sets.\n   - Website: [quizlet.com](https://quizlet.com)\n\n5. **Duolingo** - A language-learning app and website that gamifies learning new languages.\n   - Website: [duolingo.com](https://www.duolingo.com)\n\n### Research and Writing Tools\n6. **Google Scholar** - A free search engine for scholarly literature across many disciplines.\n   - Website: [scholar.google.com](https://scholar.google.com)\n\n7. **Grammarly** - A writing assistant that helps with grammar, style, and plagiarism checking.\n   - Website: [grammarly.com](https://www.grammarly.com)\n\n8. **Purdue OWL** - A comprehensive guide for writing and citation styles, especially APA and MLA.\n   - Website: [owl.purdue.edu](https://owl.purdue.edu)\n\n9. **Mendeley** - A reference manager and academic social network to organize research.\n   - Website: [mendeley.com](https://www.mendeley.com)\n\n### Study and Organizational Tools\n10. **Trello** - A project management tool that helps with organization and task management.\n    - Website: [trello.com](https://trello.com)\n\n11. **Evernote** - A note-taking application that helps organize notes, tasks, and research.\n    - Website: [evernote.com](https://www.evernote.com)\n\n12. **Google Drive** - Cloud storage that allows for collaboration on documents, spreadsheets, and presentations.\n    - Website: [drive.google.com](https://drive.google.com)\n\n### Additional Learning and Practice\n13. **Wolfram Alpha** - A computational knowledge engine that can solve mathematical problems and provide information on a variety of topics.\n    - Website: [wolframalpha.com](https://www.wolframalpha.com)\n\n14. **Codecademy** - An interactive platform that teaches coding and programming languages.\n    - Website: [codecademy.com](https://www.codecademy.com)\n\n15. **SparkNotes** - A resource for literature summaries, analysis, and study guides.\n    - Website: [sparknotes.com](https://www.sparknotes.com)\n\n16. **Brainly** - A social media platform for students to ask questions and get homework help from peers.\n    - Website: [brainly.com](https://brainly.com)\n\n### Educational Games and Quizzes\n17. **Kahoot!** - An interactive game-based learning platform to create quizzes and engage students.\n    - Website: [kahoot.com](https://kahoot.com)\n\n18. **Socrative** - A student response system that allows teachers to create quizzes and polls for real-time feedback.\n    - Website: [socrative.com](https://socrative.com)\n\n### Professional Development\n19. **LinkedIn Learning** - Offers courses on various professional skills, from software development to business skills.\n    - Website: [linkedin.com/learning](https://www.linkedin.com/learning)\n\n20. **FutureLearn** - Provides free online courses from top universities across various subjects.\n    - Website: [futurelearn.com](https://www.futurelearn.com)\n\n### General Knowledge and Exploration\n21. **TED-Ed** - Animated educational videos and lessons on a wide range of topics.\n    - Website: [ed.ted.com](https://ed.ted.com)\n\n22. **Mental Floss** - Offers fun facts and trivia on a variety of subjects to broaden general knowledge.\n    - Website: [mentalfloss.com](https://www.mentalfloss.com)\n\nThese resources can help students enhance their learning, improve their writing skills, manage their time and tasks better, and deepen their understanding of various subjects.",
